    "excerpt": "A prayer for women caught up in the torment of 'get' refusal from a husband who refuses to grant them the document required for a religious divorce. . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"/translate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contribute a translation</a></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nמִי שֶׁעָנָה לְאִמּוֹתֵינוּ שָׂרָה רִבְקָה לֵאָה וְרָחֵל,<br />\nהוּא יַעֲנֶה לַנָּשִׁים הָעֲגוּנוֹת וּמְסֹרָבוֹת הַגֵּט,<br />\nוְיִפְרֹשׂ עֲלֵיהֶן סֻכַּת שָׁלוֹם.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nיְהִי רָצוֹן<br />\nשֶׁיִּתֵּן חָכְמָה וְעֹז בְּיַד הַדַּיָּנִים<br />\nלְהַתִּירָן מִכַּבְלֵיהֶן<br />\nוִיעוֹרֵר תְּשׁוּבָה שְׁלֵמָה בְּלִבּוֹתֵיהֶם<br />\nשֶׁל הַכּוֹבְלִים אוֹתָן.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nעוֹשֶׂה שָׁלוֹם בִּמְרוֹמָיו,<br />\nהוּא יַעֲשֶׂה שָׁלוֹם עֲלֵיהֶן,<br />\nוְנֹאמַר, אָמֵן.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>&#8220;תפילה לעגונות ומסורבות הגט&#8221; by הרבה אלונה ליסיצה Rabbi Alona Lisitsa appears in <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/תפילת-האדם-סידור-רפורמי-ישראלי-101214578258569\">תפילת האדם, סידור רפורמי ישראלי</a> (2020), the Israeli Reform Movement siddur edited by Rabbi Alona Lisitsa (Ph.D.) and Rabbi Dr. Dalia Marx.</p>\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<p><span style=\"float: right;\"><div id=\"attachment_32530\" style=\"width: 170px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-0\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32530\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020-160x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"160\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32530\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020-160x300.jpg 160w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020.jpg 505w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-32530\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tefilat ha-Adam (Israeli Reform Movement, 2020)</p></div></span>  <span style=\"float: left;\"><div id=\"attachment_32718\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/tefilat-ha-adam-p.381.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32718\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/tefilat-ha-adam-p.381-300x124.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"124\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32718\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/tefilat-ha-adam-p.381-300x124.jpg 300w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/tefilat-ha-adam-p.381-1024x422.jpg 1024w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/tefilat-ha-adam-p.381.jpg 1070w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-32718\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">tefilat ha-adam p.381</p></div></span><span class=\"\" style=\"display:block;clear:both;height: 0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;\"></span></p>\n",
